OL,3,CGunman who murdered ex-prison officer
OL,4,Cin revenge shooting jailed for 45 years
OL,6,FThe killer of a former prison officer
OL,7,Foutside of a gym in Skelmersdale has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for a minimum of 45 years
OL,9,Ffor murder.
OL,11,FElias Morgan, 35 gunned down Lenny
OL,12,FScott, 33 on February 8, 2024, four
OL,13,Fyears after Mr Scott exposed an
OL,14,Fillicit affair between prisoner Morgan
OL,15,Fand a female prison guard. Scott was
OL,16,Fshot six times by Morgan who
OL,17,Fapproached him in a hi-vis jacket.
