OL,6,FPreston Crown Court heard the shooting
OL,7,Fcame after Morgan told the dad-of-
OL,8,Fthree he would "get him" after the
OL,9,Fprison officer, at HMP Altcourse near
OL,10,FLiverpool, searched his cell and found
OL,11,Fa mobile phone on March 26, 2020.
OL,13,FLenny, from Prescot, was said to have
OL,14,Frefused a bribe of #1,500 in return
OL,15,Ffor not reporting a phone which Morgan
OL,16,Fillegally held behind bars and which
OL,17,Fcontained evidence of an affair.
