OL,6,FFrom that moment, prosecuting
OL,7,Fbarrister Alex Leach KC said, Morgan
OL,8,Ftold Lenny he would get him. "He said
OL,9,Fhe would bide his time, but that he
OL,10,Fwould get him".
OL,12,FMorgan, of Edge Hill in Liverpool, was
OL,13,Ffound guilty on Friday 29 August of
OL,14,Fmurdering Lenny by an 11-person jury,
OL,15,Fconsisting of eight men and three
OL,16,Fwomen.
OL,18,FAnother man on trial with Morgan,
OL,19,FAnthony Cleary, 29, was cleared of
OL,20,Fboth murder and manslaughter.
