OL,6,FDuring the nine week trial at Preston
OL,7,FCourt Court, the jury heard a call
OL,8,FLenny made to police on 101 just days
OL,9,Fafter he had seized Morgan's iPhone,
OL,10,Fwhere he said he believed his family
OL,11,Fhome was being watched.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the call operator, the
OL,14,Fprison officer said he was in fear of
OL,15,Fhis family's safety after Morgan
OL,16,Fallegedly had men watching his house.
OL,18,F"We are so angry that Lenny was killed
OL,19,Ffor doing the right thing, doing his
OL,20,Fjob well, with pride and integrity and
OL,21,Fmaintaining his strong values.
