OL,6,F"Despite being threatened by Morgan he
OL,7,Fstuck to his values and followed
OL,8,Fprison procedure. He lost his life
OL,9,Fstanding up for what was right" she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FEx-partner Lucy Griffiths, the mother
OL,13,Fof Mr Scott's twin boys, gave a victim
OL,14,Fimpact statement in court where she
OL,15,Fdescribed him as a devoted father and
OL,16,Fa, "kind, caring and compassionate
OL,17,Fman".
