OL,6,F"He adored his children. All he ever
OL,7,Fwanted to be, was a dad. The moment he
OL,8,Fwas murdered our world came crumbling
OL,9,Fdown, my heart broke."
OL,11,FMs Griffiths said when she got the
OL,12,Ftelephone call to say Mr Scott had
OL,13,Fbeen killed, his boys were bouncing on
OL,14,Ftheir beds because he was due to visit
OL,15,Fthem that day.
OL,17,FThey still ask if they can go to see
OL,18,Fhim in heaven, Ms Griffiths said, and
OL,19,Fshe finds notes under their pillows
OL,20,Fasking him to come back home.
