OL,6,FPassing sentence Mr Justice Goose told
OL,7,Fthe defendant: "This murder was a
OL,8,Fcarefully planned, revenge killing of
OL,9,Fa prison officer. He was loved,
OL,10,Frespected and made his family proud."
OL,12,FMorgan was jailed for a minimum of 45
OL,13,Fyears.
